<H3> <TI>   Incursion Repulsed </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  NC3101195094 Yerevan ARMENPRES International Service in 
Armenian 1154 GMT 31 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC3101195094 </F>
<F P=104>  Yerevan ARMENPRES International Service </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Armenian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Yerevan, 31 Jan (ARMENPRES) -- An Azerbaijani 
reconnaissance battalion violated Armenia's borders in 
Tavushskiy Rayon and launched an attack against the defensive 
positions near Movses in the early hours of 31 January. 
  The enemy suffered human losses at the fighting, which 
continuing for a few hours, and was thrown back. There were no 
casualties on the Armenian side. 

</TEXT>

