<F P=101> Armenia </F>
<H3> <TI>   Karabakh Unions Launch Defense Fund Initiative </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  NC0102124094 Yerevan SNARK in English 0926 GMT 1 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC0102124094 </F>
<F P=104>  Yerevan SNARK </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Stepanakert, February 1 (SNARK)--Sergey Davidyan, 
chairman of the Karabakh Federation of Professional Unions, told 
SNARK the Karabakh professional unions introduce their 
initiative to transfer a part of the expenditures the 
professional unions possess to the Fund of Defence. The 
professional unions of some Karabakh enterprises and 
organizations are ready to send 20-25 per cent of the employees' 
salaries to the Fund of Defence. 
  According to Davidyan, the Karabakh people are ready to send 
food from their stores to the front. 
  During the period of last 2-3 days about 10 million rubles 
were transferred to the Fund of Defence. 

</TEXT>

