<H3> <TI>   Supreme Council Decree on Government Structure </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0102145294 Dushanbe Radio Tajikistan Network in Russian 
1000 GMT 1 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0102145294 </F>
<F P=104>  Dushanbe Radio Tajikistan Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Taking into account the proposal of chairman of the 
Tajik Council of Ministers submitted to execute the decree of 
the Supreme Council of the Republic of Tajikistan on the 
structure of the Council of Ministers, the presidium of the 
Tajik Supreme Council decreed, as an exception, the following 
structure of the Tajik Council of Ministers. 
  Chairman of the Council of Ministers of the Republic of 
Tajikistan. 
  First deputy chairman of the Council of Ministers of the 
Republic of Tajikistan. 
  Four deputy chairmen of the Council of Ministers of the 
Republic of Tajikistan. 
  Administrator of Affairs of the Council of Ministers of 
the Republic of Tajikistan. 
  Twenty two ministries, in particular: 
  The Ministry of Economy and Forecasting of the Republic of 
Tajikistan. 
  The Ministry of Finance of the Republic of Tajikistan. 
  The Ministry of Foreign Economic Relations [words 
indistinct] of the Republic of Tajikistan. 
  The Ministry of Agriculture of the Republic of Tajikistan. 
  The Ministry of Industry of the Republic of Tajikistan. 
  The Ministry of Construction of the Republic of Tajikistan 
and others. 
  The State Committees [of the Republic of Tajikistan]. 
  The State Committee of the Republic of Tajikistan on TV 
and Radio. 
  The State Committee of the Republic of Tajikistan on 
Construction and Architecture. 
  The State Committee of the Republic of Tajikistan on State 
Property. 
  The above mentioned decree will be submitted for approval at 
the regular session of the Tajik Supreme Council. 
  The full text of the ministries will be published in the 
press. 

</TEXT>

