<H3> <TI>   Supreme Council Issues Decree on Farmers Congress </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0202113594 Dushanbe Radio Tajikistan Network in Russian 
1000 GMT 2 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0202113594 </F>
<F P=104>  Dushanbe Radio Tajikistan Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The presidium of the Supreme Council of the Republic 
of Tajikistan decrees: 
  It is permitted, as an exception in conditions of a state of 
emergency, for the Union of Collective Farmers of the Republic 
of Tajikistan to hold the fifth congress of the collective 
farmers of the Republic of Tajikistan on 25-26 February in 
Dushanbe. 
  (Yoqubjon) Salimov, internal affairs minister of Tajikistan, 
and (Saidamir) Zuhurov, chairman of the National Security 
Committee of Tajikistan, are to take measures to ensure the 
security and safety of the participants in the fifth congress of 
the collective farmers of Tajikistan. 

