Language: <F P=105> Ukrainian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Unattributed report] </F>
  [Text] Ukraine and Russia have reached an agreement to 
jointly operate the Cosmic Center of Flight Control based in 
Yevpatoria, in the Crimea. Its plan of activities includes the 
Center's participation in international projects and controlling 
the flights of stations "Blyskavka," "Horyzont," "Meteor," and 
