  Shukurjon Zuhurov is appointed as the labor and employment 
minister of the Republic of Tajikistan. 
  Ibrohim Usmonov is appointed as the communication minister 
of the Republic of Tajikistan. 
  Aleksandr Shishlyannikov is appointed as the defense 
minister of the Republic of Tajikistan. 
  Yokub Salimov is appointed as the internal affairs 
minister of the Republic of Tajikistan. 
  Shavkat Ismoilov is appointed as the justice minister of 
the Republic of Tajikistan. 
  Abdusattor Jabborov is appointed as the social security 
minister of the Republic of Tajikistan. 
  Bahoviddin Zuhurddin is appointed as the chairman of the 
State Committee for Construction and Architecture of the 
Republic of Tajikistan. 
  [First name not given] Davlatov is appointed as the 
chairman of the State Committee for State Property of the 
