<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Vietnamese Foreign Minister Nguyen Manh Cam and 
Uzbek Foreign Minister Saidmukhtar Said Asymov signed a protocol 
on cooperation between the two ministries in Tashkent on 
Wednesday [2 February]. 
