  [Text] Liepaja, Latvia, Feb 02, BNS -- The Conference on 
Security and Cooperation in Europe's mission is visiting the 
Liepaja city this week to acquaint itself with the problems of 
ethnic minorities and the Russian troop withdrawal here. 
  Mission's members Jakub Volsky and Johan Olav Seland plan to 
